data.description: Welcome to a place where dreams become reality, where comfort meets elegance, and where lasting memories are made. This stunning single family home at 2364 Riva Ridge Rd in Montgomery, IL, is a testament to impeccable design and thoughtful living, offering a harmonious blend of contemporary style and suburban tranquility.    Step inside this inviting home and experience the warmth and sophistication that it exudes. The open floor plan, with 9' ceilings ,seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a spacious and inviting gathering space for family and friends. Natural light pours in through large windows, highlighting the new LVP floors and tasteful finishes.    The modern updated kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, a center island, a walk in pantry and plenty of cabinet space. Whether you're hosting a grand dinner or a casual brunch, this kitchen can handle it all.    Upstairs, you'll find four  bedrooms, each with its own unique charm and ample closet space. The master suite is a true retreat, with a walk-in closet and a private en-suite bathroom offering a soaking tub and separate shower.    Entertain to your heart's delight in this custom finished Prohibition Era style basement with extra deep pour ceilings.  Complete with faux brick walls and a secret door...    Step outside to your oversized private backyard oasis, complete with a deck and hot tub all fully fenced and accessible to the open green and view of the pond in the back.  This outdoor space is perfect for enjoying the fresh air, entertaining, or simply unwinding after a long day. Nestled in the friendly community of Montgomery, this home offers the perfect balance of suburban serenity and easy access to shopping, Oswego schools, parks, and nearby amenities. This is your chance to own a home that defines modern living in a tranquil setting. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort, elegance, and warmth that 2364 Riva Ridge Rd has to offer. Make this residence your own and begin a new chapter of cherished moments in Montgomery.
